examples.en: A turtle lays many eggs at one time.
The crocodile lays its eggs on land.
The female lays a single egg and covers it over.
Foul befalls the man who ever lays a snare in my way!
She lays the butter on so thickly that you hardly taste the bagel.
Tortoise scoops out a nesting place in the sand and lays its eggs in it.
